                <div class="row align-items-center">
                    <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-12">
                        <p>Aaron Roeck has been creating both awe and astonishment professionally for 10 years through his comedy
                            and magic. Based out of Kitchener, Aaron has performed for audiences throughout Ontario and across
                            Canada. His blend of jaw dropping magic and side-splitting humour leaves audiences both amazed and
                            hysterical throughout the performance.
                            <br>
                            <br>After seeing a magician perform as a child and being taught a few card tricks from his father, he
                            was instantly hooked by the feeling of brightening someone's day with a little laughter and amazement.
                            Although the size of audiences and the tricks have changed, his motivation remains the same whether
                            performing for 1 or 1000.
                            <br>
                            <br>Aaron is a proud father of 3 and has been married to his wife Mariah for 5 years.
                            <br>
                            <br>Allow Aaron to join you at your next event and see for yourself how magic has the ability to make
                            any event unique and memorable for all.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-12">
                        <img class="img-fluid shadow p-2 bg-white rounded" alt="Meet the Magician" src="ARM-Wedding-Close.png">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>


        <!-- Services section. -->
        <div class="section container">
            <h1 class="text-center">
                <span id="href-services"></span>Services</h1>

            <div class="row">

                <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-12">
                    <h4 class="text-center">Stage Magic Show</h2>
                        <p>This 20-60 minute comedy and magic show is excellent for after dinner entertainment where everyone
                            is seated and facing the stage. Full of audience participation, this high energy performance
                            is suitable for all ages. From living rooms to theatres to banquet halls, make your next event
                            memorable and exciting with this unique Stage Magic Show!</p>

                        <h4 class="text-center">Walk Around Magic</h2>
                            <p>Get up close and personal with walk around and close up magic. Excellent for those times where
                                guests are mingling and enjoying drinks or appetizers. Whether audiences are seated or standing
                                this style of strolling magic works great for creating a fun atmosphere and giving everyone
                                something exciting to talk about. Walk Around Magic is also very effective at cocktail parties
                                or for filling in a lull at some events such as wedding receptions, fundraisers or corporate
                                dinners.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-12">
                    <h4>Aaron's magic is fully tailorable and great for almost any event such as:</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Wedding Receptions</li>
                        <li>Corporate Events</li>
                        <li>Holiday Parties</li>
                        <li>Bar & Bat Mitzvahs</li>
                        <li>Youth Retreats & Church Functions</li>
                        <li>Fundraisers</li>
                        <li>School Events</li>
                        <li>Celebratory Milestones</li>
                        <li>Private Functions</li>
                        <li>Restaurant Entertainment</li>
                        <li>And much more!</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

            </div>

