                <div id="myCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">

                    <!-- This creates the slide # indicator on the bottom of the carousel. -->
                    <ol class="carousel-indicators">
                        <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
                        <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="1"></li>
                        <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="2"></li>
                        <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="3"></li>
                    </ol>

                    <div class="carousel-inner">
                        <!-- Each carousel item is composed of one of these blocks. -->
                        <div class="carousel-item active">
                            <div class="container">
                                <div class="carousel-caption text-left">
                                    <p>"Aaron Roeck is a top-notch magician and performer. He did a great job connecting with his
                                        audiences – both youth and adults. Everyone was laughing one minute and gasping in amazement
                                        the next! Aaron’s great personality and humour make him great on stage. Off stage he
                                        is very professional and great to be around. I highly recommend hiring him for your next
                                        event!"
