                        <div class="carousel-item">
                            <div class="container">
                                <div class="carousel-caption text-left">
                                    <p>"Having been in the wedding industry for over a decade, I highly recommend Aaron Roeck as
                                        the best "walk around" magician for wedding cocktail receptions. His appeal to young
