                                        is professional and personable. If you want to make every part of your wedding day memorable
                                        and magical, I encourage you to invite Aaron Roeck to be a part of it."
                                        <br>
                                        <br>Martti Pajunen
                                        <br>Regional Director, Kettle Creek Weddings</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="carousel-item">
                            <div class="container">
                                <div class="carousel-caption text-left">
                                    <p>"People are still raving about how awesome your show was here. You were very professional
                                        in presentation, and your tricks were amazing. Looking forward to hosting another show
                                        soon!"
                                        <br>
                                        <br>Tim Loveday
                                        <br>Bethany Church, Kitchener - ECM Camps</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="carousel-item">
                            <div class="container">
                                <div class="carousel-caption text-left">
                                    <p>"We had Aaron perform some walk around magic during the cocktail hour at our wedding. Aaron
                                        was able to take what is normally a dull part of the day for our guests and turn it into
                                        something fun and memorable! More than that, we were extremely grateful for the peace
                                        of mind knowing our guests were being entertained while we were off taking our wedding
                                        photos."
                                        <br>
                                        <br>Kelly & David Locking</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                    </div>

                    <!-- These are the carousel controls that advance to the next or previous slide when clicked. -->
                    <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#myCarousel" role="button" data-slide="prev">
